      <h3>Disclose Use of Funds</h3>
      <p>Provide a detailed description of how you intend to use the funds, so that investors have enough information to understand how the money will be used. If you have a range of possible uses, describe each probable use and the factors you'll use to choose among them. If you will accept funding in excess of the target offering amount, describe the intended use of the excess proceeds with similar specificity.</p>

